    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the meat-free mince is cooking, add the <strong>spaghetti </strong>to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the<strong> spaghetti</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite then drain and return to the pot until serving</p><p>Meanwhile, dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and <strong>soy sauce</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
